// ██████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████
// SECTION 2: CORE LOGIC - CONSTANTS, STATE VARIABLES, AND TIME
// ██████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████

// =====================================================================================================================================
// Constants
// =====================================================================================================================================
string S_STANDBY = "STANDBY"
string S_HUNTING = "HUNTING"
string S_CONFIRMING = "CONFIRMING"
string S_ARMED = "ARMED"
string CHECK = "✔"
string NO_CHECK = "☐"

// =====================================================================================================================================
// State Machine & Strategy Progress Variables (using `var` for statefulness)
// =====================================================================================================================================
var string protocolStatus = S_STANDBY
var string activeKillzone = "None"
var string activeStrategy = "None"
var bool isBullishSignal = false
var int signalBarIndex = na
var float entryPrice = na
var float stopLossPrice = na
var float takeProfitPrice = na
var int armedTrigger = 0  // Numeric variable for detecting armed state changes

// Core SMC Model State
var bool event1_manipulation = false
var bool event2_structure_break = false
var bool event3_htf_poi_return = false
var bool event4_ltf_confirmation = false

// Silver Bullet Model State
var bool sb_event1_sweep = false
var bool sb_event2_fvg = false

// Midnight Reversal Model State
var bool mrev_event1_inducement = false
var bool mrev_event2_reversal_confirm = false

// =====================================================================================================================================
// Enhanced SMC Data Structures (from Price Action Suite)
// =====================================================================================================================================
var map<string, float> bigData = map.new<string, float>()
var array<float> highArr = array.new_float()
var array<float> lowArr = array.new_float() 
var array<int> timeArr = array.new_int()
var array<float> closeArr = array.new_float()
var array<float> openArr = array.new_float()
var array<box> highBlock = array.new_box()
var array<box> lowBlock = array.new_box()
var array<label> upLabel = array.new_label(1)
var array<label> dnLabel = array.new_label(1)

// Initialize bigData map
if bigData.size() == 0
    bigData.put("moving", 0)
    bigData.put("upaxis", 0.0)
    bigData.put("upaxis2", 0)
    bigData.put("dnaxis", 0.0)
    bigData.put("dnaxis2", 0)
    bigData.put("upside", 1)
    bigData.put("downside", 1)

// Update arrays with current bar data
highArr.unshift(high)
lowArr.unshift(low)
timeArr.unshift(time)
closeArr.unshift(close)
openArr.unshift(open)

// =====================================================================================================================================
// CISD Data Structures and Variables
// =====================================================================================================================================
type cisd_bin 
    line ln 
    bool active 
    int start_index
    float start_price
    bool broken = false

type cisd_swing 
    int index
    float price
    line ln
    line wick
    bool active = false

// CISD Variables
var int cisd_trend = 0
var array<cisd_bin> cisd_bull_bins = array.new<cisd_bin>() 
var array<cisd_bin> cisd_bear_bins = array.new<cisd_bin>() 
var array<cisd_swing> cisd_swings_high = array.new<cisd_swing>() 
var array<cisd_swing> cisd_swings_low = array.new<cisd_swing>() 
var int cisd_last_ph_index = na
var float cisd_last_ph_price = na
var int cisd_last_pl_index = na
var float cisd_last_pl_price = na
var int cisd_track_bull_index = na
var float cisd_track_bull_price = na
var int cisd_track_bear_index = na
var float cisd_track_bear_price = na

var cisd_bin cisd_active_bull = cisd_bin.new(line.new(bar_index, open, bar_index, open, color=color.green), true, bar_index, high)
var cisd_bin cisd_active_bear = cisd_bin.new(line.new(bar_index, open, bar_index, open, color=color.red), true, bar_index, low)

// CISD helper variables
cisd_bull_candle = close > open 
cisd_bear_candle = close < open 
cisd_is_sweep_mode = i_cisd_method == "Liquidity Sweep"
cisd_text_size = i_cisd_label_size == "Small" ? size.small : size.tiny

// =====================================================================================================================================
// Time & Session Logic
// =====================================================================================================================================
is_time_in_range(session, tz) =>
    t = time(timeframe.period, session, tz)
    not na(t)

bool inMidnightKZ = is_time_in_range(i_midnight_session, "UTC") and i_midnight_strategy != O_OFF
bool inLondonKZ = is_time_in_range(i_london_session, "UTC") and i_london_strategy != O_OFF
bool inNewYorkKZ = is_time_in_range(i_ny_session, "UTC") and i_ny_strategy != O_OFF
bool inAnyKZ = inMidnightKZ or inLondonKZ or inNewYorkKZ

// Asian Session hardcoded for liquidity purposes
string asianSession = "0000-0700"
bool inAsianSession = is_time_in_range(asianSession, "UTC")

// ██████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████
// SECTION 3: SMC ENGINE - POINT OF INTEREST (POI) DETECTION FUNCTIONS
// ██████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████

// =====================================================================================================================================
// 3.1 Market Structure & HTF Bias
// =====================================================================================================================================
f_get_htf_bias() =>
    htf_close = request.security(syminfo.tickerid, i_htf_timeframe, close, lookahead=barmerge.lookahead_on)
    htf_ema = ta.ema(htf_close, 50)
    htf_bias = close > htf_ema ? "BULLISH" : "BEARISH"
    htf_bias

string htfBias = f_get_htf_bias()

// Swing Points Detection
f_isSwingHigh(len) =>
    high[len] == ta.highest(high, len * 2 + 1)
f_isSwingLow(len) =>
    low[len] == ta.lowest(low, len * 2 + 1)

// BOS / MSS Detection
var float lastBullishBOSPrice = na
var float lastBearishBOSPrice = na
var float lastSwingHigh = na
var float lastSwingLow = na
var float recentSwingHighForSL = na
var float recentSwingLowForSL = na

if f_isSwingHigh(5)
    lastSwingHigh := high[5]
    recentSwingHighForSL := high[5]
if f_isSwingLow(5)
    lastSwingLow := low[5]
    recentSwingLowForSL := low[5]

isBullishBOS = close > lastSwingHigh and not na(lastSwingHigh) and htfBias == "BULLISH"
isBearishBOS = close < lastSwingLow and not na(lastSwingLow) and htfBias == "BEARISH"
isBullishMSS = close > lastSwingHigh and not na(lastSwingHigh) and htfBias == "BEARISH"
isBearishMSS = close < lastSwingLow and not na(lastSwingLow) and htfBias == "BULLISH"

if isBullishBOS or isBullishMSS
    lastBullishBOSPrice := lastSwingHigh
    lastSwingHigh := na // Invalidate after break
if isBearishBOS or isBearishMSS
    lastBearishBOSPrice := lastSwingLow
    lastSwingLow := na // Invalidate after break

// =====================================================================================================================================
// Market Structure Labels
// =====================================================================================================================================
var int bullishStructureBar = na
var float bullishStructurePrice = na
var string bullishStructureText = na
var int bearishStructureBar = na
var float bearishStructurePrice = na
var string bearishStructureText = na

if i_show_bos_mss
    if ta.change(lastBullishBOSPrice)
        line.new(bar_index[1], lastBullishBOSPrice, bar_index, lastBullishBOSPrice, color=color.new(c_bullish, 50), style=line.style_dotted, width=1)
        bullishStructureBar := bar_index
        bullishStructurePrice := lastBullishBOSPrice
        bullishStructureText := isBullishBOS ? "BOS" : "MSS"

    if ta.change(lastBearishBOSPrice)
        line.new(bar_index[1], lastBearishBOSPrice, bar_index, lastBearishBOSPrice, color=color.new(c_bearish, 50), style=line.style_dotted, width=1)
        bearishStructureBar := bar_index
        bearishStructurePrice := lastBearishBOSPrice
        bearishStructureText := isBearishMSS ? "MSS" : "BOS"

if not na(bullishStructureBar) and bar_index == bullishStructureBar
    label.new(x=bullishStructureBar, y=low, yloc=yloc.belowbar, text=bullishStructureText, color=color.new(c_bullish, 0), textcolor=color.white, style=label.style_triangleup, size=size.tiny)

if not na(bearishStructureBar) and bar_index == bearishStructureBar
    label.new(x=bearishStructureBar, y=high, yloc=yloc.abovebar, text=bearishStructureText, color=color.new(c_bearish, 0), textcolor=color.white, style=label.style_triangledown, size=size.tiny)
        
// =====================================================================================================================================
// 3.2 Liquidity Detection
// =====================================================================================================================================
var float asiaHigh = na
var float asiaLow = na

int asianSessionStartBar = ta.barssince(inAsianSession and not inAsianSession[1])
int rawSessionLength = not na(asianSessionStartBar) and asianSessionStartBar >= 0 ? math.max(1, bar_index - asianSessionStartBar) : 1
int asianSessionLength = math.min(rawSessionLength, 5000)
float currentAsiaHigh = ta.highest(high, asianSessionLength)
float currentAsiaLow = ta.lowest(low, asianSessionLength)

if not inAsianSession and inAsianSession[1] and not na(asianSessionLength) and asianSessionLength > 0 and asianSessionLength <= bar_index
    asiaHigh := currentAsiaHigh[1]
    asiaLow := currentAsiaLow[1]
    
    if i_show_session_ranges and not na(asiaHigh) and not na(asiaLow)
        sessionStartBar = bar_index - asianSessionLength
        sessionEndBar = bar_index
        box.new(sessionStartBar, asiaHigh, sessionEndBar, asiaLow, border_color=na, bgcolor=c_session_range)
        line.new(sessionStartBar, asiaHigh, sessionEndBar, asiaHigh, color=c_session_range, style=line.style_dotted)
        line.new(sessionStartBar, asiaLow, sessionEndBar, asiaLow, color=c_session_range, style=line.style_dotted)

[pdh, pdl] = request.security(syminfo.tickerid, "D", [high[1], low[1]], lookahead=barmerge.lookahead_on)
isAsiaHighSweep = high > asiaHigh and not na(asiaHigh)
isAsiaLowSweep = low < asiaLow and not na(asiaLow)
isPDHSweep = high > pdh and not na(pdh)
isPDLSweep = low < pdl and not na(pdl)
isAnyLiquiditySweep = isAsiaHighSweep or isAsiaLowSweep or isPDHSweep or isPDLSweep

// =====================================================================================================================================
// 3.3 Enhanced Price Action Suite Calculations
// =====================================================================================================================================

calculatePivots(length) =>
    var int intraCalc = 0
    if bar_index > length + 1
        up = highArr.slice(0, length).max()
        dn = lowArr.slice(0, length).min() 
        cHi = highArr.get(length)
        cLo = lowArr.get(length)
        intraCalc := cHi > up ? 0 : cLo < dn ? 1 : intraCalc[1]
        topSwing = intraCalc == 0 and intraCalc[1] != 0 ? cHi : 0 
        botSwing = intraCalc == 1 and intraCalc[1] != 1 ? cLo : 0 
        [topSwing, botSwing]

[bigUpper, bigLower] = calculatePivots(i_ext_sens)
[smallUpper, smallLower] = calculatePivots(i_int_sens)

drawChar(x, y, str, col, down) =>
    style = down ? label.style_label_down : label.style_label_up
    line.new(int(x), y, bar_index, y, color=col, style=line.style_dashed)
    label.new(math.round(math.avg(x, bar_index)), y, str, color=#00000000, textcolor=col, style=style, size=size.small)

drawStructureExt() => 
    var int counter = 0
    if bigUpper != 0
        bigData.put("upside", 1)
        x1 = bar_index - i_ext_sens
        txt = bigUpper > bigData.get("upaxis") ? 'HH' : 'LH'
        if i_show_hh_lh
            upLabel.set(0, label.new(x1, bigUpper, txt, color=color.new(color.black, 100), textcolor=c_bearish, style=label.style_label_down, size=size.small))
        if i_show_ob
            highBlock.push(box.new(x1, bigUpper, last_bar_index + 5, bigUpper * .998, border_color=color.new(color.red, 75), bgcolor=color.new(color.red, 95), text="OB", text_size=size.small, text_color=color.black))
        bigData.put("upaxis", bigUpper)
        bigData.put("upaxis2", x1)
        counter := 1
    if bigLower != 0
        bigData.put("downside", 1)
        x1 = bar_index - i_ext_sens
        txt = bigLower < bigData.get("dnaxis") ? "LL" : "HL"
        if i_show_hl_ll
            dnLabel.set(0, label.new(x1, bigLower, txt, color=#ffffff00, textcolor=c_bullish, style=label.style_label_up, size=size.small))
        if i_show_ob
            lowBlock.push(box.new(x1, bigLower, last_bar_index + 5, bigLower * 1.002, border_color=color.new(color.blue, 75), bgcolor=color.new(color.blue, 95), text="OB", text_size=size.small, text_color=color.black))    
        bigData.put("dnaxis", bigLower)
        bigData.put("dnaxis2", x1)
        counter := -1
    if i_show_ext_structure
        if ta.crossover(close, bigData.get("upaxis")) and bigData.get("upside") != 0
            str = bigData.get("moving") < 0 ? i_ext_structure != "BoS" ? 'CHoCH' : "" : i_ext_structure != 'CHoCH' ? 'BoS' : ""
            if i_ext_structure == "All" or str.contains(i_ext_structure, str)
                drawChar(bigData.get("upaxis2"), bigData.get("upaxis"), str, c_bullish, true)
            bigData.put("upside", 0)
            bigData.put("moving", 1)
        if ta.crossunder(close, bigData.get("dnaxis")) and bigData.get("downside") != 0
            str = bigData.get("moving") > 0 ? i_ext_structure != "BoS" ? 'CHoCH' : "" : i_ext_structure != 'CHoCH' ? 'BoS' : ""
            if i_ext_structure == "All" or str.contains(i_ext_structure, str)
                drawChar(bigData.get("dnaxis2"), bigData.get("dnaxis"), str, c_bearish, false)
            bigData.put("downside", 0)
            bigData.put("moving", -1)
    counter 
counter = drawStructureExt()

method updateBox(array<box> id) =>
    if id.size() > 0 
        for i = 0 to id.size() - 1
            id.get(i).set_right(last_bar_index + 5)
method cleanseLevel(array<box> id, bool isHighBlock) => 
    if id.size() > 0   
        for i = id.size() - 1 to 0 
            condition = isHighBlock ? close >= id.get(i).get_top() : close <= id.get(i).get_bottom()
            if condition
                id.remove(i).delete()
        if id.size() > i_show_last and i_show_last != 0
            for i = id.size() - i_show_last to 0 
                id.remove(i).delete()
highBlock.cleanseLevel(true)
lowBlock.cleanseLevel(false)

if barstate.islast
    highBlock.updateBox()
    lowBlock.updateBox()

fvg(direction) => 
    var fvgMat = matrix.new<float>(5)
    var fvgDrawings = array.new<box>()
    var fvgMidLines = array.new<line>()
    fvgMat.add_col(0, array.from(math.sign(close - open), close, high, low, time))
    if fvgMat.columns() > 3 
        fvgMat.remove_col(fvgMat.columns() - 1)
    if fvgMat.row(0).sum() == direction
        getDir = math.sign(direction)
        y = getDir == -1 ? fvgMat.get(3, 2) : fvgMat.get(3, 0)
        y1 = getDir == -1 ? fvgMat.get(2, 0) : fvgMat.get(2, 2)
        col = i_close_only_fvg ? #00000000 : color.new(c_fvg, i_fvg_transparency)
        fvgDrawings.push(box.new(int(fvgMat.get(4, 1)), y, last_bar_time, y1, xloc=xloc.bar_time, border_color=col, bgcolor=col, text="FVG", text_size=size.small, text_color=color.black))
        fvg_midpoint = math.avg(y, y1)
        midline_color = i_close_only_fvg ? color.new(color.gray, 0) : color.new(c_fvg, math.max(0, i_fvg_transparency - 30))
        fvgMidLines.push(line.new(int(fvgMat.get(4, 1)), fvg_midpoint, last_bar_time, fvg_midpoint, xloc=xloc.bar_time, color=midline_color, style=line.style_dotted, width=1))
    [fvgDrawings, fvgMidLines]

if i_show_fvg
    [fvgDn, fvgDnLines] = fvg(-3)
    [fvgUp, fvgUpLines] = fvg(3)
    if fvgDn.size() > 0 
        for i = fvgDn.size() - 1 to 0
            getfvg = fvgDn.get(i)
            if high >= getfvg.get_top()
                getfvg.delete()
                fvgDn.remove(i)
                if fvgDnLines.size() > i
                    fvgDnLines.get(i).delete()
                    fvgDnLines.remove(i)
            else if i_contract_fvg and high > getfvg.get_bottom()
                getfvg.set_bottom(high)
                if fvgDnLines.size() > i
                    new_midpoint = math.avg(getfvg.get_top(), getfvg.get_bottom())
                    fvgDnLines.get(i).set_y1(new_midpoint)
                    fvgDnLines.get(i).set_y2(new_midpoint)
    if fvgUp.size() > 0 
        for i = fvgUp.size() - 1 to 0
            getfvg = fvgUp.get(i)
            if low <= getfvg.get_bottom()
                getfvg.delete()
                fvgUp.remove(i)
                if fvgUpLines.size() > i
                    fvgUpLines.get(i).delete()
                    fvgUpLines.remove(i)
            else if i_contract_fvg and low < getfvg.get_top()
                getfvg.set_top(low)
                if fvgUpLines.size() > i
                    new_midpoint = math.avg(getfvg.get_top(), getfvg.get_bottom())
                    fvgUpLines.get(i).set_y1(new_midpoint)
                    fvgUpLines.get(i).set_y2(new_midpoint)
    if i_close_only_fvg and barstate.islast 
        minDist = matrix.new<float>(1, 2, 20e20)
        if fvgDn.size() > 0 
            for i = fvgDn.size() - 1 to 0
                getBottom = fvgDn.get(i).get_bottom()
                minDist.set(0, 1, math.min(minDist.get(0, 1), math.abs(close - getBottom)))
                if math.abs(close - getBottom) == minDist.get(0, 1)
                    minDist.set(0, 0, i)
                fvgDn.get(i).set_right(fvgDn.get(i).get_left())
                if fvgDnLines.size() > i
                    fvgDnLines.get(i).set_x2(fvgDnLines.get(i).get_x1())
            closest_dn_idx = int(minDist.get(0, 0))
            fvgDn.get(closest_dn_idx).set_bgcolor(color.new(c_fvg, i_fvg_transparency))
            fvgDn.get(closest_dn_idx).set_border_color(color.new(c_fvg, i_fvg_transparency))
            fvgDn.get(closest_dn_idx).set_right(last_bar_time)
            if fvgDnLines.size() > closest_dn_idx
                fvgDnLines.get(closest_dn_idx).set_color(color.new(c_fvg, math.max(0, i_fvg_transparency - 30)))
                fvgDnLines.get(closest_dn_idx).set_x2(last_bar_time)
        minDist.set(0, 0, 0)
        minDist.set(0, 1, 20e20)
        if fvgUp.size() > 0 
            for i = fvgUp.size() - 1 to 0
                getTop = fvgUp.get(i).get_top()
                minDist.set(0, 1, math.min(minDist.get(0, 1), math.abs(close - getTop)))
                if math.abs(close - getTop) == minDist.get(0, 1)
                    minDist.set(0, 0, i)
                fvgUp.get(i).set_right(fvgUp.get(i).get_left())
                if fvgUpLines.size() > i
                    fvgUpLines.get(i).set_x2(fvgUpLines.get(i).get_x1())
            closest_up_idx = int(minDist.get(0, 0))
            fvgUp.get(closest_up_idx).set_bgcolor(color.new(c_fvg, i_fvg_transparency))
            fvgUp.get(closest_up_idx).set_border_color(color.new(c_fvg, i_fvg_transparency))
            fvgUp.get(closest_up_idx).set_right(last_bar_time)
            if fvgUpLines.size() > closest_up_idx
                fvgUpLines.get(closest_up_idx).set_color(color.new(c_fvg, math.max(0, i_fvg_transparency - 30)))
                fvgUpLines.get(closest_up_idx).set_x2(last_bar_time)

var line main = line.new(0, 0, 100, 100, style=line.style_dashed, width=2)
method updateMain(line id) =>
    if i_show_fibs
        [bigUpperFibs, bigLowerFibs] = calculatePivots(25)
        var int counterFibs = 0
        if bigUpperFibs != 0
            counterFibs := 1
        if bigLowerFibs != 0
            counterFibs := -1
        if counterFibs == 1
            hi = 0.0
            lo = 1e8
            id.set_xy1(int(bigData.get("upaxis2")), bigData.get("upaxis"))
            for i = 0 to bar_index - int(bigData.get("dnaxis2"))
                getLow = lowArr.get(i)
                lo := math.min(getLow, lo)
                if lo == getLow
                    id.set_xy2(bar_index - i, lo)
        else if counterFibs == -1
            hi = 0.0
            lo = 1e8
            id.set_xy1(int(bigData.get("dnaxis2")), bigData.get("dnaxis"))
            for i = 0 to bar_index - bigData.get("upaxis2")
                getHigh = highArr.get(i)
                hi := math.max(highArr.get(i), hi)
                if hi == getHigh
                    id.set_xy2(bar_index - i, hi)
        if id.get_x2() < id.get_x1()
            x1_val = id.get_x1()
            y1_val = id.get_y1()
            x2_val = id.get_x2()
            y2_val = id.get_y2()
            id.set_xy1(x2_val, y2_val)
            id.set_xy2(x1_val, y1_val)
        id.set_color(id.get_y2() < id.get_y1() ? c_bearish : c_bullish)
    0
main.updateMain()

quickLine(getX2, y, color) => line.new(getX2, y, bar_index + 5, y, color=color.new(color, 75))
quickLabel(y, txt, color) => label.new(bar_index + 5, y, text=str.tostring(txt), color=#00000000, style=label.style_label_left, textcolor=color)

drawFibs() => 
    if barstate.islast
        var fibLine = array.new<line>(5)
        var fibLab = array.new<label>(5) 
        if fibLine.size() > 0 
            for i = 0 to fibLine.size() - 1
                fibLine.get(i).delete()
                fibLab.get(i).delete()
        if i_show_fibs
            getY2 = main.get_y2()
            sub = main.get_y1() - getY2
            getX2 = main.get_x2()
            for i = 0 to fibLine.size() - 1
                mod = i % fibLine.size() - 1   
                [y, col, txt] = switch mod
                    0 => [sub * i_fib1 + getY2, i_show_236 ? i_fib1_col : color.new(chart.bg_color, 100), i_fib1]
                    1 => [sub * i_fib2 + getY2, i_show_382 ? i_fib2_col : color.new(chart.bg_color, 100), i_fib2]
                    2 => [sub * i_fib3 + getY2, i_show_5 ? i_fib3_col : color.new(chart.bg_color, 100), i_fib3]
                    3 => [sub * i_fib4 + getY2, i_show_618 ? i_fib4_col : color.new(chart.bg_color, 100), i_fib4]
                    => [sub * i_fib5 + getY2, i_show_786 ? i_fib5_col : color.new(chart.bg_color, 100), i_fib5] 
                fibLine.set(i, quickLine(getX2, y, col))
                fibLab.set(i, quickLabel(y, txt, col))
drawFibs()

drawAOE() => 
    if i_show_aoe and closeArr.size() > 50
        aoi = closeArr.slice(0, 50) 
        aoi2 = openArr.slice(0, 50) 
        maxaoiH = math.max(aoi.max(), aoi2.max())
        minaoiL = math.min(aoi.min(), aoi2.min())
        var aoeLevels = map.new<string, box>()
        if aoeLevels.size() == 0 
            aoeLevels.put("High", box.new(bar_index[50], maxaoiH * 1.01, bar_index + 5, maxaoiH, border_color=#00000000, bgcolor=color.new(c_bearish, 90), text="Area of Interest", text_size=size.small, text_color=color.new(c_bearish, 33)))
            aoeLevels.put("Low", box.new(bar_index[50], minaoiL, bar_index + 5, minaoiL * .99, border_color=#00000000, bgcolor=color.new(c_bullish, 90), text="Area of Interest", text_size=size.small, text_color=color.new(c_bullish, 33)))
        getHighBox = aoeLevels.get("High")
        if close <= getHighBox.get_top() * 1.01
            getHighBox.set_lefttop(bar_index[50], maxaoiH + ta.atr(14))
            getHighBox.set_rightbottom(bar_index + 5, maxaoiH)
            getHighBox.set_text("Area of Interest")
        else 
            getHighBox.set_lefttop(bar_index + 5, maxaoiH + ta.atr(14))
            getHighBox.set_rightbottom(bar_index + 5, maxaoiH + ta.atr(14))
            getHighBox.set_text("")
        getLowBox = aoeLevels.get("Low")
        if close >= getLowBox.get_bottom() * .99
            getLowBox.set_lefttop(bar_index[50], minaoiL)
            getLowBox.set_rightbottom(bar_index + 5, minaoiL - ta.atr(14))
            getLowBox.set_text("Area of Interest")
        else 
            getLowBox.set_lefttop(bar_index + 5, minaoiL)
            getLowBox.set_rightbottom(bar_index + 5, minaoiL - ta.atr(14))
            getLowBox.set_text("")
drawAOE()

var bool isBullish_ICHoch = false
var bool isBearish_ICHoch = false

drawStructureInternals() =>
    if i_show_int_structure
        var keyValues = map.new<string, float>()
        if keyValues.size() == 0
            keyValues.put("movingSmall", 0)
        if smallUpper != 0
            keyValues.put("upsideSmall", 1)
            keyValues.put("upaxisSmall", smallUpper)
            keyValues.put("upaxis2Small", bar_index - i_int_sens)
        if smallLower != 0
            keyValues.put("downsideSmall", 1)
            keyValues.put("dnaxisSmall", smallLower)
            keyValues.put("dnaxis2Small", bar_index - i_int_sens)

        bullish_str = ""
        bearish_str = ""

        if ta.crossover(close, keyValues.get("upaxisSmall")) and keyValues.get("upsideSmall") != 0
            bullish_str := keyValues.get("movingSmall") < 0 ? (i_int_structure != "BoS" ? 'I-CHoCH' : "") : (i_int_structure != "CHoCH" ? 'I-BoS' : "")
            if i_int_structure == "All" or str.contains(i_int_structure, bullish_str)
                drawChar(keyValues.get("upaxis2Small"), keyValues.get("upaxisSmall"), bullish_str, c_bullish, true)
            keyValues.put("upsideSmall", 0)
            keyValues.put("movingSmall", 1)

        if ta.crossunder(close, keyValues.get("dnaxisSmall")) and keyValues.get("downsideSmall") != 0
            bearish_str := keyValues.get("movingSmall") > 0 ? (i_int_structure != "BoS" ? 'I-CHoCH' : "") : (i_int_structure != "CHoCH" ? 'I-BoS' : "")
            if i_int_structure == "All" or str.contains(i_int_structure, bearish_str)
                drawChar(keyValues.get("dnaxis2Small"), keyValues.get("dnaxisSmall"), bearish_str, c_bearish, false)
            keyValues.put("downsideSmall", 0)
            keyValues.put("movingSmall", -1)
        [bullish_str, bearish_str]
    else
        ["", ""]

[bull_str, bear_str] = drawStructureInternals()

isBullish_ICHoch := bull_str == 'I-CHoCH'
isBearish_ICHoch := bear_str == 'I-CHoCH'

if i_show_cisd
    ph = ta.pivothigh(i_cisd_swing_length, 1)
    pl = ta.pivotlow(i_cisd_swing_length, 1)
    if not na(ph) 
        cisd_swings_high.push(cisd_swing.new(bar_index - 1, ph))
        cisd_last_ph_index := bar_index - 1
        cisd_last_ph_price := ph
    if not na(pl) 
        cisd_swings_low.push(cisd_swing.new(bar_index - 1, pl))
        cisd_last_pl_index := bar_index - 1
        cisd_last_pl_price := pl
    if cisd_bull_candle and cisd_bear_candle[1]
        cisd_track_bull_index := bar_index
        cisd_track_bull_price := open
    if cisd_bear_candle and cisd_bull_candle[1]
        cisd_track_bear_index := bar_index
        cisd_track_bear_price := open
    if not na(cisd_last_ph_price) and close > cisd_last_ph_price
        cisd_last_ph_index := na
        cisd_last_ph_price := na
    if not na(cisd_last_pl_price) and close < cisd_last_pl_price
        cisd_last_pl_index := na
        cisd_last_pl_price := na
    if not cisd_is_sweep_mode      
        if barstate.isconfirmed and cisd_bull_candle and cisd_bear_candle[1]
            if cisd_active_bull.active and not cisd_active_bull.broken
                cisd_active_bull.ln.delete()
            cisd_active_bull.active := true
            cisd_active_bull.ln := line.new(cisd_track_bull_index, cisd_track_bull_price, bar_index, cisd_track_bull_price, color=color.new(i_cisd_bull_color, 40))
            cisd_active_bull.start_index := not na(cisd_last_ph_index) ? cisd_last_ph_index : bar_index
            cisd_active_bull.start_price := not na(cisd_last_ph_price) ? cisd_last_ph_price : high
            cisd_active_bull.broken := false
        if barstate.isconfirmed and cisd_bear_candle and cisd_bull_candle[1] 
            if cisd_active_bear.active and not cisd_active_bear.broken
                cisd_active_bear.ln.delete()
            cisd_active_bear.active := true
            cisd_active_bear.ln := line.new(cisd_track_bear_index, cisd_track_bear_price, bar_index, cisd_track_bear_price, color=color.new(i_cisd_bear_color, 40))
            cisd_active_bear.start_index := not na(cisd_last_pl_index) ? cisd_last_pl_index : bar_index
            cisd_active_bear.start_price := not na(cisd_last_pl_price) ? cisd_last_pl_price : low
            cisd_active_bear.broken := false
        if cisd_active_bull.active and bar_index - cisd_active_bull.ln.get_x1() <= i_cisd_max_validity
            cisd_active_bull.ln.set_x2(bar_index)
            if close < cisd_active_bull.ln.get_y2()
                if bar_index - cisd_active_bull.ln.get_x1() >= i_cisd_min_duration
                    cisd_active_bull.ln.set_color(i_cisd_bear_color)
                    if cisd_trend == -1
                        cisd_active_bull.ln.set_style(line.style_dashed)
                    cisd_active_bull.active := false
                    cisd_active_bull.broken := true
                    cisd_trend := -1
                    x = math.ceil(math.avg(cisd_active_bull.ln.get_x1(), bar_index))
                    label.new(x, cisd_active_bull.ln.get_y2(), style=label.style_label_up, textcolor=i_cisd_bear_color, text='CISD', size=cisd_text_size, color=color.new(color.white, 100)) 
                else 
                    cisd_active_bull.active := false
                    cisd_active_bull.ln.delete()
        else if cisd_active_bull.active
            cisd_active_bull.active := false
            cisd_active_bull.ln.delete()
        if cisd_active_bear.active and bar_index - cisd_active_bear.ln.get_x1() <= i_cisd_max_validity          
            cisd_active_bear.ln.set_x2(bar_index)
            if close > cisd_active_bear.ln.get_y2()  
                if bar_index - cisd_active_bear.ln.get_x1() >= i_cisd_min_duration 
                    cisd_active_bear.ln.set_color(i_cisd_bull_color)
                    if cisd_trend == 1
                        cisd_active_bear.ln.set_style(line.style_dashed)
                    cisd_active_bear.active := false
                    cisd_active_bear.broken := true
                    cisd_trend := 1
                    x = math.ceil(math.avg(cisd_active_bear.ln.get_x1(), bar_index))
                    label.new(x, cisd_active_bear.ln.get_y2(), style=label.style_label_down, textcolor=i_cisd_bull_color, text='CISD', color=color.new(color.white, 100), size=cisd_text_size) 
                else
                    cisd_active_bear.active := false
                    cisd_active_bear.ln.delete()
        else if cisd_active_bear.active
            cisd_active_bear.active := false
            cisd_active_bear.ln.delete()
    else 
        if cisd_swings_high.size() > 0 
            for i = cisd_swings_high.size() - 1 to 0 
                get = cisd_swings_high.get(i)
                x = get.index
                y = get.price
                if bar_index - x > i_cisd_max_validity 
                    cisd_swings_high.remove(i)
                else if not na(get.ln)
                    if close > get.ln.get_y2()
                        cisd_swings_high.remove(i)
                    else if close > y
                        cisd_swings_high.remove(i)
                    else if not get.active and high > get.price and close < get.price
                        get.ln := line.new(x, get.price, bar_index, get.price, color=i_cisd_sweep_color)
                        get.wick := line.new(bar_index, get.price, bar_index, high, color=i_cisd_sweep_color, width=3)
                        get.active := true
                        if not na(cisd_track_bull_index) and not na(cisd_track_bull_price)
                            cisd_bull_bins.push(cisd_bin.new(line.new(cisd_track_bull_index, cisd_track_bull_price, bar_index, cisd_track_bull_price, color=color.new(i_cisd_bull_color, 40)), true, cisd_track_bull_index, cisd_track_bull_price))
        if cisd_swings_low.size() > 0 
            for i = cisd_swings_low.size() - 1 to 0 
                get = cisd_swings_low.get(i)
                x = get.index
                y = get.price
                if bar_index - x > i_cisd_max_validity 
                    cisd_swings_low.remove(i)
                else if not na(get.ln)
                    if close < get.ln.get_y2()
                        cisd_swings_low.remove(i)
                    else if close < y
                        cisd_swings_low.remove(i)
                    else if not get.active and low < get.price and close > get.price
                        get.ln := line.new(x, get.price, bar_index, get.price, color=i_cisd_sweep_color)
                        get.wick := line.new(bar_index, get.price, bar_index, low, color=i_cisd_sweep_color, width=3)
                        get.active := true
                        if not na(cisd_track_bear_index) and not na(cisd_track_bear_price)
                            cisd_bear_bins.push(cisd_bin.new(line.new(cisd_track_bear_index, cisd_track_bear_price, bar_index, cisd_track_bear_price, color=color.new(i_cisd_bear_color, 40)), true, cisd_track_bear_index, cisd_track_bear_price))
        if cisd_bull_bins.size() > 0 
            for i = cisd_bull_bins.size() - 1 to 0 
                get = cisd_bull_bins.get(i)
                get.ln.set_x2(bar_index)
                x1 = get.ln.get_x1()
                if bar_index - x1 > i_cisd_max_validity
                    get.ln.delete(), cisd_bull_bins.remove(i) 
                else if close < get.ln.get_y2() 
                    if bar_index - x1 >= i_cisd_min_duration
                        get.ln.set_color(i_cisd_bear_color)
                        if cisd_trend == -1
                            get.ln.set_style(line.style_dashed)
                        cisd_trend := -1 
                        x = math.ceil(math.avg(x1, bar_index))
                        label.new(x, get.ln.get_y2(), style=label.style_label_up, textcolor=i_cisd_bear_color, text='CISD', size=cisd_text_size, color=color.new(color.white, 100))
                        label.new(bar_index, high, style=label.style_label_down, textcolor=i_cisd_bear_color, text='▼', size=cisd_text_size, color=color.new(color.white, 100))
                    else 
                        get.ln.delete()
                    cisd_bull_bins.remove(i)
        if cisd_bear_bins.size() > 0 
            for i = cisd_bear_bins.size() - 1 to 0 
                get = cisd_bear_bins.get(i)
                get.ln.set_x2(bar_index)
                x1 = get.ln.get_x1()
                if bar_index - x1 > i_cisd_max_validity
                    get.ln.delete(), cisd_bear_bins.remove(i) 
                else if close > get.ln.get_y2() 
                    if bar_index - x1 >= i_cisd_min_duration
                        get.ln.set_color(i_cisd_bull_color)
                        if cisd_trend == 1
                            get.ln.set_style(line.style_dashed)
                        cisd_trend := 1 
                        x = math.ceil(math.avg(x1, bar_index))
                        label.new(x, get.ln.get_y2(), style=label.style_label_down, textcolor=i_cisd_bull_color, text='CISD', size=cisd_text_size, color=color.new(color.white, 100))
                        label.new(bar_index, low, style=label.style_label_up, textcolor=i_cisd_bull_color, text='▲', size=cisd_text_size, color=color.new(color.white, 100))
                    else 
                        get.ln.delete()
                    cisd_bear_bins.remove(i)

var float confirmedBullishIFVGLevel = na
var float confirmedBearishIFVGLevel = na

isBullishIFVG_simple = low[2] > high[0] and low < low[2] and close > low[2]
isBearishIFVG_simple = high[2] < low[0] and high > high[2] and close < high[2]

if isBullishIFVG_simple
    confirmedBullishIFVGLevel := low[2]
if isBearishIFVG_simple
    confirmedBearishIFVGLevel := high[2]

f_detect_smt() =>
    [corr_h, corr_l] = request.security(i_corr_asset_ticker, timeframe.period, [high, low])
    main_higher_high = high > high[1]
    corr_lower_high = corr_h < corr_h[1]
    main_lower_low = low < low[1]
    corr_higher_low = corr_l > corr_l[1]
    is_bearish_smt = main_higher_high and corr_lower_high
    is_bullish_smt = main_lower_low and corr_higher_low
    [is_bullish_smt, is_bearish_smt]

[isBullishSMT, isBearishSMT] = f_detect_smt()
isAnySMT = isBullishSMT or isBearishSMT

// ██████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████
// SECTION 4: STATE MACHINE & STRATEGY LOGIC
// ██████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████

// --- CRITICAL FIX v3.4: Complete rewrite of State Machine Logic ---

// 1. Reset all event flags at the start of each new bar's script execution.
// This prevents states from carrying over incorrectly between bars.
event1_manipulation := false, event2_structure_break := false, event3_htf_poi_return := false, event4_ltf_confirmation := false
sb_event1_sweep := false, sb_event2_fvg := false
// Note: mrev flags are handled by their persistent 'var' declarations and reset below.

// 2. Determine the current state based on time.
if inAnyKZ
    // If we just entered a Killzone, switch to HUNTING and reset all strategy progress.
    if protocolStatus == S_STANDBY
        protocolStatus := S_HUNTING
        mrev_event1_inducement := false
        mrev_event2_reversal_confirm := false
        activeKillzone := "None" // Force re-evaluation of the active killzone
        activeStrategy := "None"
else
    // If we are outside any killzone, always be in STANDBY.
    protocolStatus := S_STANDBY
    activeKillzone := "None"
    activeStrategy := "None"

// 3. If a trade was ARMED and the killzone has now ended, reset to STANDBY.
if protocolStatus == S_ARMED and not inAnyKZ
    protocolStatus := S_STANDBY
    activeKillzone := "None"
    activeStrategy := "None"
        
// 4. Determine active strategy ONLY when HUNTING for the first time in a session.
if protocolStatus == S_HUNTING and activeKillzone == "None"
    if inMidnightKZ
        activeKillzone := "Midnight"
        activeStrategy := i_midnight_strategy
    else if inLondonKZ
        activeKillzone := "London"
        activeStrategy := i_london_strategy
    else if inNewYorkKZ
        activeKillzone := "New York"
        activeStrategy := i_ny_strategy

// 5. Main Strategy Logic execution block
if activeStrategy != O_OFF and protocolStatus != S_STANDBY
    
    // --- Strategy Module C: "The Midnight Reversal" ---
    if activeStrategy == O_MIDNIGHT
        // State 1: HUNTING for Inducement (Event 1)
        if protocolStatus == S_HUNTING
            if htfBias == "BULLISH" and ta.change(cisd_trend) and cisd_trend == -1
                mrev_event1_inducement := true // Set the persistent flag
                protocolStatus := S_CONFIRMING     // Change state
                isBullishSignal := true
            if htfBias == "BEARISH" and ta.change(cisd_trend) and cisd_trend == 1
                mrev_event1_inducement := true // Set the persistent flag
                protocolStatus := S_CONFIRMING     // Change state
                isBullishSignal := false
        
        // State 2: CONFIRMING - waiting for Reversal (Event 2)
        else if protocolStatus == S_CONFIRMING
            if isBullishSignal and ((ta.change(cisd_trend) and cisd_trend == 1) or isBullish_ICHoch)
                mrev_event2_reversal_confirm := true
                protocolStatus := S_ARMED
                entryPrice := close
                stopLossPrice := recentSwingLowForSL
                signalBarIndex := bar_index
                armedTrigger += 1
            if not isBullishSignal and ((ta.change(cisd_trend) and cisd_trend == -1) or isBearish_ICHoch)
                mrev_event2_reversal_confirm := true
                protocolStatus := S_ARMED
                entryPrice := close
                stopLossPrice := recentSwingHighForSL
                signalBarIndex := bar_index
                armedTrigger += 1

    // --- Strategy Module A: "The Core SMC Model" ---
    if activeStrategy == O_CORE
        // This is a multi-step confirmation, so we'll use a temporary state tracker
        var int core_model_step = 0

        // Step 0 -> 1: Manipulation
        if core_model_step == 0 and (isAnyLiquiditySweep or isAnySMT)
            event1_manipulation := true
            protocolStatus := S_CONFIRMING
            core_model_step := 1
        
        // Step 1 -> 2: Structure Break
        if core_model_step == 1 and (isBullishMSS or isBearishMSS or isBullishBOS or isBearishBOS)
            event2_structure_break := true
            isBullishSignal := isBullishMSS or isBullishBOS
            core_model_step := 2
            
        // Step 2 -> 3: Return to POI
        if core_model_step == 2
            if isBullishSignal and lowBlock.size() > 0
                if low <= lowBlock.last().get_top()
                    event3_htf_poi_return := true
                    core_model_step := 3
            if not isBullishSignal and highBlock.size() > 0
                if high >= highBlock.last().get_bottom()
                    event3_htf_poi_return := true
                    core_model_step := 3
        
        // Step 3 -> 4: LTF Confirmation -> ARMED
        if core_model_step == 3
            if isBullishSignal and isBullishIFVG_simple
                event4_ltf_confirmation := true
                protocolStatus := S_ARMED
                entryPrice := confirmedBullishIFVGLevel
                stopLossPrice := recentSwingLowForSL
                signalBarIndex := bar_index
                armedTrigger += 1
            if not isBullishSignal and isBearishIFVG_simple
                event4_ltf_confirmation := true
                protocolStatus := S_ARMED
                entryPrice := confirmedBearishIFVGLevel
                stopLossPrice := recentSwingHighForSL
                signalBarIndex := bar_index
                armedTrigger += 1
        
        // Reset steps if killzone ends
        if protocolStatus == S_HUNTING
            core_model_step := 0
            
    // --- Strategy Module B: "ICT Silver Bullet" ---
    if activeStrategy == O_SILVER
        var bool silver_bullet_step1 = false
        if not silver_bullet_step1 and isAnyLiquiditySweep
            sb_event1_sweep := true
            protocolStatus := S_CONFIRMING
            isBullishSignal := low < pdl or low < asiaLow
            silver_bullet_step1 := true
        
        else if silver_bullet_step1
            [currentFVGUp, _] = fvg(3)
            [currentFVGDn, _] = fvg(-3)
            if isBullishSignal and currentFVGUp.size() > 0
                sb_event2_fvg := true
                protocolStatus := S_ARMED
                entryPrice := currentFVGUp.last().get_bottom()
                stopLossPrice := recentSwingLowForSL
                signalBarIndex := bar_index
                armedTrigger += 1
            if not isBullishSignal and currentFVGDn.size() > 0
                sb_event2_fvg := true
                protocolStatus := S_ARMED
                entryPrice := currentFVGDn.last().get_top()
                stopLossPrice := recentSwingHighForSL
                signalBarIndex := bar_index
                armedTrigger += 1
        
        if protocolStatus == S_HUNTING
            silver_bullet_step1 := false


// ██████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████
// SECTION 5: ON-CHART DASHBOARD & VISUALS
// ██████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████

var table dashboard = table.new(position.top_right, 2, 13, bgcolor=#20222C, border_color=#363843, frame_color=#363843, border_width=1, frame_width=1)
nyHour = hour(timenow, "America/New_York"), nyMinute = minute(timenow, "America/New_York")
calculateTimeDifference(timestamp1, timestamp2) =>
    timeDifference = timestamp2 - timestamp1
    hours = math.floor(timeDifference / 3600000)
    minutes = math.floor((timeDifference % 3600000) / 60000)
    [hours, minutes]
dayAdjustment = (hour(timenow, "America/New_York") < 2) ? dayofmonth(timenow) + 1 : dayofmonth(timenow)
timeIsInRange(startHour, startMinute, endHour, endMinute) =>
    (nyHour > startHour or (nyHour == startHour and nyMinute >= startMinute)) and (nyHour < endHour or (nyHour == endHour and nyMinute <= endMinute))
[chartcol, timetilchange, stringCol, stringCol2] = switch 
    timeIsInRange(9, 30, 16, 0) => [#f24968, timestamp("America/New_York", year(timenow), month(timenow), dayofmonth(timenow), 16, 0, 0), "New York", "Asia"]
    timeIsInRange(20, 0, 2, 0) => [#14D990, timestamp("America/New_York", year(timenow), month(timenow), dayAdjustment, 2, 0, 0), "Asia", "London"]
    timeIsInRange(3, 0, 11, 30) => [#F2B807, timestamp("America/New_York", year(timenow), month(timenow), dayofmonth(timenow), 11, 30, 0), "London", "New York"]
    => [color.gray, int(na), "Dead Zone", (nyHour > 16 or nyHour < 3) ? "London" : (nyHour >= 11 and nyHour < 20) ? "Asia" : "New York"]
[hours, minutes] = calculateTimeDifference(timenow, timetilchange)
timetilchange2 = switch
    timeIsInRange(9, 30, 16, 0) => timestamp("America/New_York", year(timenow), month(timenow), dayofmonth(timenow), 20, 0, 0) 
    timeIsInRange(20, 0, 2, 0) => timestamp("America/New_York", year(timenow), month(timenow), dayofmonth(timenow), 3, 0, 0)  
    timeIsInRange(3, 0, 11, 30) => timestamp("America/New_York", year(timenow), month(timenow), dayofmonth(timenow), 9, 30, 0) 
    => na 
if na(timetilchange2)
    timetilchange2 := switch
        nyHour < 9 or (nyHour == 9 and nyMinute < 30) => timestamp("America/New_York", year(timenow), month(timenow), dayofmonth(timenow), 9, 30, 0) 
        nyHour < 20 or (nyHour >= 16 and nyHour < 20) => timestamp("America/New_York", year(timenow), month(timenow), dayofmonth(timenow), 20, 0, 0) 
        nyHour < 3 or (nyHour >= 2 and nyHour < 3) => timestamp("America/New_York", year(timenow), month(timenow), dayofmonth(timenow), 3, 0, 0)     
        => na  
[hours2, minutes2] = calculateTimeDifference(timenow, timetilchange2)

if barstate.islast
    table.cell(dashboard, 0, 0, "APEX PROTOCOL", text_color=color.white, text_size=size.normal, text_halign=text.align_left)
    table.merge_cells(dashboard, 0, 0, 1, 0)
    table.cell(dashboard, 0, 1, "Status:", text_color=c_dashboard_header, text_halign=text.align_left)
    table.cell(dashboard, 1, 1, protocolStatus, text_color=protocolStatus == S_ARMED ? color.green : c_dashboard_text, text_halign=text.align_left, text_size=size.normal)
    table.cell(dashboard, 0, 2, "HTF Bias:", text_color=c_dashboard_header, text_halign=text.align_left)
    table.cell(dashboard, 1, 2, htfBias, text_color=htfBias == "BULLISH" ? c_bullish : c_bearish, text_halign=text.align_left)
    table.cell(dashboard, 0, 3, "Session:", text_color=c_dashboard_header, text_halign=text.align_left)
    table.cell(dashboard, 1, 3, stringCol, text_color=c_dashboard_text)
    table.cell(dashboard, 0, 4, "Session Close:", text_color=c_dashboard_header, text_halign=text.align_left)
    table.cell(dashboard, 1, 4, stringCol != "Dead Zone" ? str.tostring(hours) + "h " + str.tostring(minutes) + "m" : "Dead Zone", text_color=c_dashboard_text)
    table.cell(dashboard, 0, 5, "Next Session:", text_color=c_dashboard_header, text_halign=text.align_left)
    table.cell(dashboard, 1, 5, stringCol2, text_color=c_dashboard_text)
    table.cell(dashboard, 0, 6, "Next Session Open:", text_color=c_dashboard_header, text_halign=text.align_left)
    table.cell(dashboard, 1, 6, str.tostring(hours2) + "h:" + str.tostring(minutes2) + "m", text_color=c_dashboard_text)
    table.cell(dashboard, 0, 7, " ")
    table.merge_cells(dashboard, 0, 7, 1, 7)
    table.cell(dashboard, 0, 8, "▼ " + activeStrategy + " CHECKLIST", text_color=c_dashboard_header, text_size=size.small, text_halign=text.align_left)
    table.merge_cells(dashboard, 0, 8, 1, 8)
    
    if activeStrategy == O_MIDNIGHT
        table.cell(dashboard, 0, 9, (mrev_event1_inducement ? CHECK : NO_CHECK) + " E1: Inducement Confirmed", text_color=c_dashboard_text, text_halign=text.align_left, text_size=size.small)
        table.merge_cells(dashboard, 0, 9, 1, 9)
        table.cell(dashboard, 0, 10, (mrev_event2_reversal_confirm ? CHECK : NO_CHECK) + " E2: Reversal Confirmed", text_color=c_dashboard_text, text_halign=text.align_left, text_size=size.small)
        table.merge_cells(dashboard, 0, 10, 1, 10)
    else if activeStrategy == O_CORE
        table.cell(dashboard, 0, 9, (event1_manipulation ? CHECK : NO_CHECK) + " E1: Manipulation", text_color=c_dashboard_text, text_halign=text.align_left, text_size=size.small)
        table.merge_cells(dashboard, 0, 9, 1, 9)
        table.cell(dashboard, 0, 10, (event2_structure_break ? CHECK : NO_CHECK) + " E2: Structure Break", text_color=c_dashboard_text, text_halign=text.align_left, text_size=size.small)
        table.merge_cells(dashboard, 0, 10, 1, 10)
        table.cell(dashboard, 0, 11, (event3_htf_poi_return ? CHECK : NO_CHECK) + " E3: Return to HTF POI", text_color=c_dashboard_text, text_halign=text.align_left, text_size=size.small)
        table.merge_cells(dashboard, 0, 11, 1, 11)
        table.cell(dashboard, 0, 12, (event4_ltf_confirmation ? CHECK : NO_CHECK) + " E4: LTF Confirmation", text_color=c_dashboard_text, text_halign=text.align_left, text_size=size.small)
        table.merge_cells(dashboard, 0, 12, 1, 12)
    else if activeStrategy == O_SILVER
        table.cell(dashboard, 0, 9, (sb_event1_sweep ? CHECK : NO_CHECK) + " E1: Liquidity Sweep", text_color=c_dashboard_text, text_halign=text.align_left, text_size=size.small)
        table.merge_cells(dashboard, 0, 9, 1, 9)
        table.cell(dashboard, 0, 10, (sb_event2_fvg ? CHECK : NO_CHECK) + " E2: Displacement FVG", text_color=c_dashboard_text, text_halign=text.align_left, text_size=size.small)
        table.merge_cells(dashboard, 0, 10, 1, 10)
    else
        table.cell(dashboard, 0, 9, "No active strategy in this Killzone.", text_color=color.gray, text_halign=text.align_left, text_size=size.small)
        table.merge_cells(dashboard, 0, 9, 1, 9)

nyHour2 = hour(time, "America/New_York"), nyMinute2 = minute(time, "America/New_York")
timeIsInRange2(startHour, startMinute, endHour, endMinute) =>
    if endHour >= startHour
        (nyHour2 > startHour or (nyHour2 == startHour and nyMinute2 >= startMinute)) and (nyHour2 < endHour or (nyHour2 == endHour and nyMinute2 <= endMinute))
    else
        (nyHour2 > startHour or (nyHour2 == startHour and nyMinute2 >= startMinute)) or (nyHour2 < endHour or (nyHour2 == endHour and nyMinute2 <= endMinute))

bgcolor(timeIsInRange2(9, 30, 16, 0) ? color.new(i_ny_col, i_session_transparency) : na)
bgcolor(timeIsInRange2(20, 0, 2, 0) ? color.new(i_asia_col, i_session_transparency) : na)
bgcolor(timeIsInRange2(3, 0, 11, 30) ? color.new(i_london_col, i_session_transparency) : na)
        
f_draw_trade_visuals(entry, sl, tp, isBull) =>
    risk_distance = math.abs(entry - sl)
    if not na(risk_distance) and risk_distance > 0
        line.new(signalBarIndex, entry, bar_index + 20, entry, color=c_entry, width=2)
        line.new(signalBarIndex, sl, bar_index + 20, sl, color=c_stop_loss, style=line.style_dashed, width=1)
        line.new(signalBarIndex, tp, bar_index + 20, tp, color=c_take_profit, style=line.style_dashed, width=1)
        label.new(signalBarIndex, entry, " Entry", color=color.new(c_entry, 100), textcolor=c_entry, style=label.style_label_right)
        label.new(signalBarIndex, sl, " SL", color=color.new(c_stop_loss, 100), textcolor=c_stop_loss, style=label.style_label_right)
        label.new(signalBarIndex, tp, " TP", color=color.new(c_take_profit, 100), textcolor=c_take_profit, style=label.style_label_right)
if protocolStatus == S_ARMED and bar_index == signalBarIndex
    riskDistance = math.abs(entryPrice - stopLossPrice)
    if isBullishSignal
        takeProfitPrice := entryPrice + (riskDistance * i_rr_ratio)
    else
        takeProfitPrice := entryPrice - (riskDistance * i_rr_ratio)
    if barstate.islast
        f_draw_trade_visuals(entryPrice, stopLossPrice, takeProfitPrice, isBullishSignal)
if protocolStatus == S_ARMED and not na(signalBarIndex) and barstate.islast
    f_draw_trade_visuals(entryPrice, stopLossPrice, takeProfitPrice, isBullishSignal)

// ██████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████
// SECTION 6: ALERTING MECHANISM
// ██████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████

if protocolStatus == S_ARMED and ta.change(armedTrigger)
    alert(str.format("APEX: {0} '{1}' {2} Signal! Entry: {3}, SL: {4}, TP: {5}", activeKillzone, activeStrategy, isBullishSignal ? "BUY" : "SELL", str.tostring(entryPrice, '#.#####'), str.tostring(stopLossPrice, '#.#####'), str.tostring(takeProfitPrice, '#.#####')), alert.freq_once_per_bar_close)
